frames.caption: Miniature workers in blue overalls and yellow helmets are constructing a dessert made of banana slices and powdered sugar. The scene is set on a tart, with some workers climbing a ladder while others arrange banana slices. A large banana looms in the background, adding a whimsical touch to the scene.
frames.description: The image depicts a playful and imaginative scene where miniature figures are engaged in building a dessert. The setting is a tabletop, with a focus on the creative use of food items to mimic a construction site.

frames.caption: The image depicts a whimsical scene where miniature construction workers are assembling a dessert made of banana slices and powdered sugar. The workers, dressed in blue overalls and yellow hard hats, are carefully stacking banana slices on a tart base. The scene is set against a backdrop of large bananas, adding to the playful scale of the composition.
frames.description: This scene creatively combines elements of construction and dessert-making, featuring miniature figures engaged in building a banana tart. The setting is imaginative, with oversized bananas providing a surreal backdrop.
